{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "6b8ab56c-d658-4e83-9f77-b199792d0141", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/6b8ab56c-d658-4e83-9f77-b199792d0141@1.pkg/1772597618793/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597619693", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/6b8ab56c-d658-4e83-9f77-b199792d0141@1.pkg/1772597618793/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597619693"}, "identifier": "6b8ab56c-d658-4e83-9f77-b199792d0141", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>善用法律要求依法维权（教材“保留证据+法定途径”）。应先求助成年人（②），再报警取证（①），最后平台举报（④）；③可能侵犯隐私且不利取证。</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p>初中生小芳遭遇网络猥亵后，正确的维权步骤是（　）**&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp; ①保留聊天记录并报警&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp; ②告知父母或信任的成年人&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp; ③在社交媒体曝光对方信息&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp; ④向平台举报违规账号&nbsp;</p>\n", "title": "初中生小芳遭遇网络猥亵后，正确的维权步骤是（　）**    ①保留聊天记录并报警    ②告知父母或信任的成年人    ③在社交媒体曝光对方信息    ④向平台举报违规账号 ", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["B"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/6b8ab56c-d658-4e83-9f77-b199792d0141@1.pkg/item.json?v=1755225667186", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows":